title: SET_AUDIO_SUBMIX_EFFECT_PARAM_FLOAT
content:
0x9A209B3C// SetAudioSubmixEffectParamFloat
void SET_AUDIO_SUBMIX_EFFECT_PARAM_FLOAT(int submixId, int effectSlot, int paramIndex, float paramValue);Parameters:submixId: The submix.effectSlot: The effect slot for the submix. It is expected that the effect is set in this slot beforehand.paramIndex: The parameter index for the effect.paramValue: The parameter value to set.Sets a floating-point parameter for a submix effect.
